类 Bean

org.giiwa.dao.Bean

直接已知子类:
_Cache, _CPU, _DB, _Disk, _DiskIO, _File, _FIO, _Mem, _Mem2, _MQ, _Net, Access, AccessLog, App, AuthToken, AutoBackup, Code, Data, DemoTest, Disk, Global, GLog, History, License, Local, Menu, Message, Node, Policy, Repo.Entity, Role, Role.RoleAccess, Roles, S, Session.SID, Stat, User, User.Lock, User.UserRole, UserConfig, UserGroup
public class Bean extends Object implements Map<String,Object>, Serializable, Cloneable
The Bean Class is entity class that mapping to a table,
work with Helper, you can load/update/delete data from DB(RDS/Mongo), almost includes all methods that need for database
